sentence: LGTM, basically we need to carry around the pointers to the leaves we have already visited, and discard any new leaf that has the same pointer. The overall logic stays the same with this extra check to avoid the leaf duplicates.; I shared some more ROOT files with @imaxoi to test his code with other trees.
